casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Douglas Martin FREDERICK, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159367
COA: 345123 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the December 27, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the question presented should be reviewed by this Court.
